{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, deep network-based models such as CaffeNet, GoogLeNet, and VGG16 have significantly improved the classification accuracy compared to traditional algorithms.",
    "Additionally, some enhanced deep learning-based methods have shown even better performance than these popular deep networks.",
    "Comparable classification accuracy is achieved by some other deep learning-based methods, such as EfficientNetB3-Attn-2, L2RCF, and RSSCNet.",
    "However, the proposed model outperforms all algorithms, exhibiting remarkable classification accuracy.",
    "When the training ratios are 80%, the proposed model achieves overall accuracies of 97%."
  ]
}